 "768312218730772", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031436_768312222064105_2483983745682146754_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=AS4KuDhjG3UQ7kNvgFLJi43&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDPgiUxlJHoXU-6DL5lGLcBuOUk1evj4AJh22Pe3z3pkA&oe=66DC539E"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240210-1504414_2.png", "id": "1144388200046417", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003227_1144388210046416_8982093088097178928_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2sTB-wLG91EQ7kNvgGii2g6&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD9lZlBL4gmEqQTmtWwjqCxXeHSnxGv5oxRrgUWaQ_Adg&oe=66DC2C91"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240210-115437.png", "id": "1405118490144295", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75230048_1405118493477628_4689660376237645316_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=tsn188m5Vb0Q7kNvgFM__ni&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCigBAvBnSqVL408fTr6Xun5-rjmp_j_X6gModpLZufXg&oe=66DC3C9B"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240209-2137122.png", "id": "7621650634553270", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75556799_7621650644553269_1655627145384024300_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=IQb8eykdu9oQ7kNvgG_l4NV&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYACDoBliu9eTcCg9zlFj5wMzidT6fc0WdvVz_rn2e7dIg&oe=66DC329D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Project_Y: Working Title", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This game is the Japanese version.\nIt supports Japanese only.\n\n\"A true ghost story told by a person named Y.\nIt was about an investigation to find out the true meaning of a common self-inflicted urban legend that says, ``If you hear it, you'll be cursed.''\nand...\nThere is a ``sinister existence'' that appears and disappears there.\nThis project reconstructed those interview records as 360\u00b0 videos and produced and developed them as interactive content using live-action VR.\n\n\n- It comes with \"\